title: Flexense DiskBoss Ultimate v6.7.16
description:
Flexense DiskBoss Ultimate v6.7.16

6-Apr-2016 - DiskBoss v6.7 adds the ability to categorize and filter file search, classification and disk change monitoring results by the top-level directory name. In addition, the new product version adds the ability to preserve the file creation, modification and last access dates in file synchronization operations, improves the DiskBoss command line utility and fixes a number of bugs.

DiskBoss is an automated, rule-based data management solution allowing one to perform disk space utilization analysis, file classification, duplicate files search and cleanup, high-speed file synchronization and data migration, bulk file delete and secure data wiping, disk change monitoring, automated, policy-based file management and much more.
 
http://www.diskboss.com/
